OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FA former Royal Navy petty officer
OL,8,Fjailed for life for the murder of two
OL,9,Fyoung men sexually assaulted four
OL,10,Fother males including a 14-year-old
OL,11,Fboy in the 1990s, two of whom he had
OL,12,Fconsidered killing, a court has heard.
OL,14,FAllan Grimson was sentenced in 2001
OL,15,Ffor the murders of Nicholas Wright, a
OL,16,Fsailor, and Sion Jenkins in the late
OL,17,F1990s, Winchester Crown Court heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
