FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FThe 66-year-old is now on trial for
OL,8,Fthe rape and indecent assault of a
OL,9,Fteenage naval rating and indecent
OL,10,Fassault charges against three other
OL,11,Fmale complainants dating between
OL,12,FFebruary 1994 and November 1999.
OL,14,FJohn Price KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,15,Fjury that when Grimson was interviewed
OL,16,Fabout the case of Mr Wright in 1999,
OL,17,Fhe provided details about some of the
OL,18,Falleged offences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FHe is accused of the indecent assault
OL,8,Fof the first victim between February
OL,9,F28 and December 31 1994 and of the
OL,10,Fsecond victim between September 30 and
OL,11,FDecember 1 1998.
OL,13,FThe defendant is accused of the rape
OL,14,Fand five indecent assault offences
OL,15,Fagainst the third complainant between
OL,16,FFebruary 1 and November 30 1999.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FHe also faces four counts of indecent
OL,8,Fassault and a charge of taking an
OL,9,Findecent photograph of the fourth
OL,10,Fcomplainant, the 14-year-old child,
OL,11,Fbetween March 26 and October 31 1999.
OL,13,FMr Price said the third complainant
OL,14,Fwas a 17-year-old naval rating when he
OL,15,Fmet the defendant, aged in his late
OL,16,F30s at the time and working as an
OL,17,Finstructor at the Royal Navy
OL,18,FFirefighting School on Horsea Island
OL,19,Fin Portsmouth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said: "That posting
OL,8,Fbrought Mr Grimson into contact with
OL,9,Fmany young males aged in their late
OL,10,Fteens, novices in the naval service
OL,11,Fsubject to a regime of strict
OL,12,Fdiscipline and over every one of whom
OL,13,FAllan Grimson exercised great
OL,14,Fauthority by reason of his status in
OL,15,Fthat service.
OL,17,F"He was a big powerful man and, within
OL,18,Fthe service, admired as a capable
OL,19,Finstructor."
OL,26,@oD@VOUyD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FMr Price told the jury that the
OL,8,Fcomplainant stated that Grimson raped
OL,9,Fand sexually assaulted him when he
OL,10,Freturned to the defendant's flat in
OL,11,FPortsmouth following a night at the
OL,12,FJoanna's nightclub on the seafront.
OL,14,FThe prosecutor said that the fourth
OL,15,Fcomplainant was a 14-year-old boy from
OL,16,Fthe north east of England who had
OL,17,Fvisited Grimson at his flat in
OL,18,FPortsmouth where he indecently
OL,19,Fassaulted him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FMr Price said that in a police
OL,8,Finterview in December 1999, Grimson
OL,9,F"described what he did to (the boy)
OL,10,Fand he told police how (the boy) had
OL,11,Fasked him to stop doing what he was
OL,12,Fdoing and he told police this had made
OL,13,Fhim angry.
OL,15,F"He said if others had not known that
OL,16,F(the boy) was there with him, he would
OL,17,Fprobably have killed him.
OL,19,F"He said the anger had left him as
OL,20,Fquickly as it had come on, once he
OL,21,Frealised he couldn't kill (the boy)."
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FMr Price said that when police first
OL,8,Finterviewed the boy at his school, the
OL,9,Fcomplainant denied that anything had
OL,10,Fhappened with the defendant but after
OL,11,FGrimson was sentenced to life
OL,12,Fimprisonment for the two murders, he
OL,13,Ftelephoned police and gave new
OL,14,Finterviews detailing the allegations
OL,15,Fagainst him.
OL,17,FThe prosecutor said that when asked
OL,18,Fwhy he had changed his account, the
OL,19,Fboy, now aged 16, replied: "Cause I
OL,20,Fsafe."
OL,26,@{D@\OU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FMr Price said: "If anybody was ever
OL,8,Ftempted to suppose that Allan Grimson
OL,9,Fwas exaggerating for effect when he
OL,10,Fspoke of considering killing (the boy)
OL,11,Fwhen (the boy) protested, they would
OL,12,Fneed to re-evaluate that once knowing
OL,13,Fthat Allan Grimson pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fmurdering those two men.
OL,16,F"That he had killed them in his flat
OL,17,Fat 143A London Road having invited
OL,18,Fthem to go there with him and that on
OL,19,FAllan Grimson's own accounts, the
OL,20,Fkillings had occurred amidst sexual
OL,21,Fassaults by him upon them both."
OL,26,@oD@POUxD@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782848908
OL,3,CRoyal Navy petty officer double
OL,4,Cmurderer 'sexually assaulted four
OL,5,Cmales'
OL,7,FThe prosecutor added that Grimson had
OL,8,Ftold police of his "frustration" that
OL,9,Fthe second complainant had "left the
OL,10,Fflat alive".
OL,12,FMr Price also told the jury that
OL,13,FGrimson had told the third complainant
OL,14,Fthat a baseball bat in his flat was
OL,15,Fhis "pride and joy" and added that the
OL,16,Fdefendant had admitted to police that
OL,17,Fhe had used a baseball bat to murder
OL,18,Fthe two men.
OL,20,FGrimson, of Hollesley, Suffolk, denies
OL,21,Fthe charges and the trial continues.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@`O]qD@\OUrD@KO]wD@EOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
